videoSnippet.title: Monster of Norway | Carlsen vs Aronian | Norway Championship 2018 | Round 3
videoSnippet.description:
#agadmator Check out agadmator's chess Channel Song here https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ApkShmA65qg&t=3s

Magnus Carlsen vs Levon Aronian
Altibox Norway (2018), rd 3, May-30 
Spanish Game: Berlin Defense. Rio Gambit Accepted (C67)

1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bb5 Nf6 4. O-O Ne4 5. Re1 Nd6 6. Ne5 Be7 7. Bf1 Ne5 8. Re5 O-O 9. d4 Bf6 10. Re1 Nf5 11. d5 Re8 12. Re8 Qe8 13. Qd3 d6 14. Nd2 Bg5 15. Nf3 Bc1 16. Rc1 Bd7 17. Re1 Qd8 18. Qc4 g6 19. h3 Ng7 20. Re3 a5 21. a4 Ne8 22. Qd4 Ng7 23. g4 c6 24. c4 Ne8 25. Qf4 Kg7 26. Rb3 Rb8 27. Ng5 Nf6 28. Rf3 h6 29. Ne4 Ne4 30. Qf7 Kh8 31. Qg6
